data.title: Category:Modules
data.text:
Before making changes in the Module area, all users should review the important Module Section Information at least once (last updated Apr 10 2021)

Additionally, designers should probably also review the information How to Create a Module Page before getting started and uploading their files if they are unfamiliar with wiki editing or the Module page structure (last updated May 25 2024 - template info update)

You must be logged in to see email addresses on module pages. If you are looking for a module maintainer's address, e.g., but don't see one, ensure you are logged in first.

Thanks, The VASSAL Team
